{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew that people who were sent away hadn't come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they didn't know that there were death camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This we really were not in the know-how and ignorant about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew about Dachau-- all these camps that the Germans opened already for their own people and for-- and for-- in Germany, where they sent all the unwanted ones they'd already they sent to Dachau and the terrible things they do to their own people that were against regime.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We followed all of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- and we, we also heard about the terrible things that were happening in, in occupied France, you know, because people smuggled through in, in the locomotives in the-- under the coals, you know, were hidden there with families, and came through to the demarcation line, you know, that that-- we heard all those horrible stories, that husbands were taken away and shot, that Resistance were taken and, and, and, and were caught.",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because my brother wanted to go in the Resistance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother wouldn't let him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know if she was right or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But she couldn't cope with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after the war, we heard that some of his school friends who had joined the Maquis-- because we were very near the Maquis-- were unfortunately caught and, and, and, and tortured and killed that way.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They are horrible stories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But here, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we somehow-- we managed-- with all the fear we had and all the problems we had, we tried to survive, you understand?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We managed to get the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We managed to get some food that-- we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we were young people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were always hungry because the bread ration was very, very small-- I think one pound of bread for six people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the rest, the fat-- there was no fat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no butter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People that were the black-- could buy the black market, they probably had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, there were all the people who collaborated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Am I speaking about '40 or '42 because now the whole of France is occupied?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- when we arrived there, although there was no food till '42, we were-- we only knew what was happening in the occupied France.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it mustn't forget that in November '42, the whole of France was occupied.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then that was a different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We still didn't wear a Star of David, which means that you were not necessarily recognized.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think, as we came from Lorraine, the people in the building didn't even know we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that we were Lorrains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they came from Alsace-Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were refugees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's about all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think they knew we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We frequented Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, you see, you had to be very careful to go to other people's houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother had friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were Hungarian-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she went there from time to time to visit these people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, when it became a little bit dangerous, she wouldn't go anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the thing was that she had a coal merchant in the same building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had a ration of ration cards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And our ration cards, we got plenty of wine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are not-- we are not big wine drinkers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother bartered her wine for coals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was only June.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she wanted some to make a reserve in case we wouldn't be able to go out-- that we should have coals in the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we wouldn't be-- we could be hidden and not go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is by being in that house and coming out of that house from the coal merchant that the Milice, you know, in civilian clothes-- they-- wasn't it-- the Gestapo employed Milice.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or, you know, the Vichy government employed Milice-- that they stopped my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- they were going to arrest this Hungarian family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother found herself in that building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they're asking for her identity card-- of course, it was a ration card-- there was 'Jew' on it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, and she had on her six cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how they-- that's how they eventually caught us, all of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they arrested my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they arrested the Hungarian lady and her son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the father wasn't home yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was coming home from work, and he saw me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He waited for me in the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, don't go home, he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Your mother has been arrested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I had two younger brothers at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was out in the country to find food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My oldest brother was in hospital for an operation.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
